The paper discusses the potential of using blockchain technology for biometrics, which involves security and cryptography (cs.CR), as well as information theory (cs.IT) and computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper touches on the challenges of combining these two technologies, which could fall under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CY) and software engineering (cs.SE).
